  "detailed_description": "[/url]\n\nPROĆEMON is a retro-style procedurally generated monster collecting game. Everything is a glitch, all the time.\n\n[img width=\"600\" height=\"60\"][/img]\n\nEvery monster is procedurally generated and totally unique. All sprites, stats, flavor text, and attack moves are totally random.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\nFuse two Proćemon to make a new powerful Proćemon!\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\n[img width=\"600\" height=\"60\"][/img]\n\nUse the [b]Procedural Generator[/b] to journey to new worlds.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" mp4=\"\" webm=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\n[b]Battle enemies[/b] to level up your Proćemon or [b]charm enemies[/b] into joining your team. Every move, animation, sound, and special effect is procedurally generated.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\nEarn [b]badges [/b] by defeating the [b]Shareholders[/b] of the evil [b]Infinity Corporation[/b].\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid<br><br>PROĆEMON is a retro-style procedurally generated monster collecting game. Everything is a glitch, all the time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/4ac364ae45138976a1c0f75ab0053737.webp?t=1677880705\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br>Every monster is procedurally generated and totally unique. All sprites, stats, flavor text, and attack moves are totally random.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/315cd335923fde55338f80d3125aac5b.poster.avif?t=1677880705\" width=480 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/315cd335923fde55338f80d3125aac5b.webm?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/315cd335923fde55338f80d3125aac5b.mp4?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fuse two Proćemon to make a new powerful Proćemon!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/b4720ee4f537dc3663d35f62e54fea48.poster.avif?t=1677880705\" width=480 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/b4720ee4f537dc3663d35f62e54fea48.webm?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/b4720ee4f537dc3663d35f62e54fea48.mp4?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/85df97e7df4dec04e7a89720b99a077d.webp?t=1677880705\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br>Use the <strong>Procedural Generator</strong> to journey to new worlds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/a666e89ada1718f1bbb7ddee55f9f1ab.poster.avif?t=1677880705\" width=480 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/a666e89ada1718f1bbb7ddee55f9f1ab.webm?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/a666e89ada1718f1bbb7ddee55f9f1ab.mp4?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Battle enemies</strong> to level up your Proćemon or <strong>charm enemies</strong> into joining your team. Every move, animation, sound, and special effect is procedurally generated.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/65304bdc7a28acf7050212e886ccc0bb.poster.avif?t=1677880705\" width=480 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/65304bdc7a28acf7050212e886ccc0bb.webm?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/65304bdc7a28acf7050212e886ccc0bb.mp4?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Earn <strong>badges </strong> by defeating the <strong>Shareholders</strong> of the evil <strong>Infinity Corporation</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/dd056b1cc5180e9da6eb30c0a8776375.poster.avif?t=1677880705\" width=480 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/dd056b1cc5180e9da6eb30c0a8776375.webm?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/dd056b1cc5180e9da6eb30c0a8776375.mp4?t=1677880705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "[/url]\n\nPROĆEMON is a retro-style procedurally generated monster collecting game. Everything is a glitch, all the time.\n\n[img width=\"600\" height=\"60\"][/img]\n\nEvery monster is procedurally generated and totally unique. All sprites, stats, flavor text, and attack moves are totally random.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\nFuse two Proćemon to make a new powerful Proćemon!\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\n[img width=\"600\" height=\"60\"][/img]\n\nUse the [b]Procedural Generator[/b] to journey to new worlds.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" mp4=\"\" webm=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\n[b]Battle enemies[/b] to level up your Proćemon or [b]charm enemies[/b] into joining your team. Every move, animation, sound, and special effect is procedurally generated.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid]\n\nEarn [b]badges [/b] by defeating the [b]Shareholders[/b] of the evil [b]Infinity Corporation[/b].\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"432\"][/imgvid<br><br>PROĆEMON is a retro-style procedurally generated monster collecting game. Everything is a glitch, all the time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/4ac364ae45138976a1c0f75ab0053737.webp?t=1677880705\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br>Every monster is procedurally generated and totally unique. All sprites, stats, flavor text, and attack moves are totally random.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058380/extras/315cd335923fde55338f80d3125aac5b.poster.avif?t=1677880705\" width=480 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset